        <profileDesc>
            <creation/>
            <abstract>

                <p>The 13 miracles of John the Baptist that seem to built up a common collection, most of the stories relate about miracles
                  that took place in Ethiopia. They

                  are different from those included
                in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/VNQUDS5T"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Tarraqan2003GadlaYohannes"/><title level="m">ገድለ ዮሐንስ መጥምቅ በግእዝና በአማርኛ &lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;(&lt;/hi&gt;Gadla Yoḥannǝs Maṭmǝq bagǝʾǝzǝnnā baʾamārǝññā).&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, ‘The Acts of John the Baptist, in Gǝʾǝz and Amharic’)&lt;/hi&gt;</title><editor><t:name xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Makwannǝn Ambarbar Śǝgate, &lt;i&gt;Malʿaka bǝrhānāt&lt;/i&gt;</t:name></editor><pubPlace>ʾAddis ʾAbabā</pubPlace><publisher>n.pub.</publisher><date>2003</date></bibl>.</p>
            </abstract>
